												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Karlach hands off the metal to Dammon (off screen), and he takes it (off screen - this can stay bronze).\r\n\r\nHe forges the metal (CINE NOTE: See HAV_TieflingSurvivors_Weaponsmith, which already has animations for this that we can use here)"
